title.narrative: Procurement of Services - Technical Assistance for KESSP (Kenya Education Sector Support Programme)

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Services - Technical Assistance for KESSP (Kenya Education Sector Support Programme)) is a component of kenya education sector support programme (kessp) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £2,127,974. This component benefits Kenya, and works in the following sector(s): Education policy and administrative management, Education facilities and training, Primary education, Basic life skills for youth and adults. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development, Harewelle International Limited, IMC Worldwide. The start date is 01-07-2005 and the end date is 31-03-2011.
